    "description" : {
      "en" : "BiodivRisk-Onto provides a formal OWL 2 DL representation of the semantic relations between four international biodiversity risk disclosure frameworks — TNFD, CSRD/ESRS E4, SBTN and GRI 101 — with particular attention to the data gaps arising from GBIF/OBIS sampling bias in Latin America and the Caribbean (LAC)."
    },
    "comments" : {
      "en" : "Prototype v0.1.0. Developed as part of the paper submitted to AMW 2026."
    },
